        <num>CC 1981</num>
        <heading>1981.  Rights of beneficiary and stipulator</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1981.  Rights of beneficiary and stipulator
The stipulation gives the third-party beneficiary the right to demand performance
from the promisor.
Also the stipulator, for the benefit of the third-party beneficiary, may demand
performance from the promisor.</p>
        </content>
